    <description>Allows users to manage and reconcile bulk payment batches and accurately allocate payments to related invoices. Use Payment Studio to load payments from a single bank transaction. Use Payments &amp; Credits to load individual payments per invoice.
Population Requirement Details: Conditionally Required if legacy data loading is required.
Steps for loading data with trigger turned ON
1. Load the Payment Studio record.
2. Create Payment Line Items with Invoices allocated with Payment Studio association
3. Approve the Payment Studio record.
4. System will autocreate the Payment &amp; Credit records asscoaited with each selected invoice.
[MODULE: Finance]
[LOAD: Yes]
[PREREQUISITES: Invoice (Approved Status), If the Source Source = Cash Payment, Invoice. If the Payment Source is not equal to &apos;Cash&apos; then the below are required., Invoice, Letter of Credit, Payable, Security Deposit]
[REPLACEMENT OBJECT API: NA]
[COMMENTS: NA]</description>
